OL,3,CBlue Islands customers left camping
OL,4,Covernight in Guernsey airport
OL,6,FBlue Islands passengers on the late
OL,7,FGuernsey to Jersey flight last night
OL,8,Fsay they are appalled after being left
OL,9,Fwithout anywhere to sleep when the
OL,10,Fstorm cancelled their journey.
OL,12,F19 passengers were affected and nine
OL,13,Fended up sleeping at the airport with
OL,14,Fthe island's hotels booked up.
OL,16,FThis morning they finally returned by
OL,17,Fferry at their own expense as the next
OL,18,Favailable flight was not until
OL,19,Ftomorrow.
