OL,3,CBlue Islands customers left camping
OL,4,Covernight in Guernsey airport
OL,6,FThey claim Blue Islands still haven't
OL,7,Fcontacted them.
OL,9,FTina Caldeira from Jersey and Nikolas
OL,10,FAppleman from The Netherlands were
OL,11,Famong those who found themselves
OL,12,Fwithout accomodation for the night.
OL,14,FThey say if it was not for the kind
OL,15,Fnature if the airport staff, they
OL,16,Fwould not have had so much as a
OL,17,Fsleeping bag.
OL,19,F"I think it's appalling and I think we
OL,20,Fall felt it was appalling there was no
OL,21,Fcontact from (Blue Islands).
