OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F381A1725895240
OL,3,CBlue Islands customers left camping
OL,4,Covernight in Guernsey airport
OL,6,F"I don't think they even knew that
OL,7,Fthey had passengers left behind who
OL,8,Fhad nowhere to go and we could have
OL,9,Fbeen unable to help ourselves in any
OL,10,Fway - we really deserve to be looked
OL,11,Fafter."
OL,13,FBlue Islands customer Nikolas Appleman
OL,14,Fsaid: "I didn't get a message from
OL,15,FBlue Islands. Not a message, an SMS or
OL,16,Fan email so I was informed by my
OL,17,Ffellow passengers."
