OL,3,CBlue Islands customers left camping
OL,4,Covernight in Guernsey airport
OL,6,F"The passengers from the cancelled
OL,7,Finter-island flight to Jersey were
OL,8,Funderstandably upsetJand some were
OL,9,Funable to secure accommodation for the
OL,10,Fnight at short notice.
OL,12,F"Our teams acted quickly to make sure
OL,13,Fthese passengers were well looked
OL,14,Fafter and had aJsafe place to rest
OL,15,Fovernight.
OL,17,FA few members of our team had to stay
OL,18,Fat the airport overnight themselves,
OL,19,Ffor safety reasons, and others did not
OL,20,Freturn home until after midnight.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOU
