OL,3,CBlue Islands customers left camping
OL,4,Covernight in Guernsey airport
OL,6,F"I would like to personally thank them
OL,7,Ffor their dedication and duty of care
OL,8,Fin challengingJcircumstances.
OL,10,FIn a statement Blue Islands said: "The
OL,11,Finter-island service on Saturday
OL,12,Fevening (7 September) was disrupted
OL,13,Fdue to severe thunderstorms over
OL,14,FJersey at around the time of the
OL,15,Fdeparture from Jersey to Guernsey.
OL,17,F"Hotels in Guernsey were full, our
OL,18,Fairport representatives explored other
OL,19,Foptions with local authorities,
OL,20,Fhowever no alternative accommodation
OL,21,Foptions were available.
