OL,3,CBlue Islands customers left camping
OL,4,Covernight in Guernsey airport
OL,6,F"We thank Guernsey Airport for keeping
OL,7,Fthe terminal open and providing
OL,8,Fprovisions for passengers.
OL,10,F"Disruption is the last resort,
OL,11,Fhowever safety of our passengers, crew
OL,12,Fand aircraft is always our number one
OL,13,Fpriority. While these circumstances
OL,14,Fwere out of our control we apologise
OL,15,Ffor the inconvenience."
